---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Purchase Conditions | fashionCulture">
    <main>
        <section class="purchase-conditions-section">
            <h1>Purchase Conditions</h1>

            <div class="content-block">
                <p>
                    Welcome to fashionCulture. Please read these Purchase Conditions carefully before placing your order. By making a purchase, you agree to the terms outlined below.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Order Process</h2>
                <p>
                    When you place an order on our website, you will receive an email confirmation. This confirmation does not constitute acceptance of your order, but rather a confirmation that we have received it. All orders are subject to availability and acceptance by fashionCulture.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order for any reason, including but not limited to product availability, errors in the description or price of the product, or an error in your order.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Pricing and Payment</h2>
                <p>
                    All prices displayed on our website are in [Currency] and include any applicable taxes. We strive to ensure that all pricing information is accurate; however, errors may occur. If we discover an error in the price of any item you have ordered, we will inform you as soon as possible and give you the option to reconfirm your order at the correct price or cancel it.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We accept a variety of payment methods, including credit cards, debit cards, and [other payment options]. Payment is taken at the time of order placement. If we are unable to fulfill your order, we will issue a full refund to your original payment method.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Shipping and Delivery</h2>
                <p>
                    fashionCulture ships to various locations. Shipping costs and delivery times vary depending on the destination and shipping method selected at checkout. Estimated delivery times are provided as a guide and are not guaranteed. Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a shipping confirmation email with tracking information.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please note that we are not responsible for delays caused by customs or other factors beyond our control.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Returns and Exchanges</h2>
                <p>
                    Our return policy allows you to return items within 30 days of receiving your order. Please refer to our <a href="/return-policy">Return Policy</a> for detailed information on how to process a return. We do not offer direct exchanges. If you wish to exchange an item, please return the original item and place a new order.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p>
                    All content on the fashionCulture website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of fashionCulture or its content suppliers and is protected by international copyright laws. You may not use, reproduce, or distribute any of the content without our express written permission.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Governing Law</h2>
                <p>
                    These Purchase Conditions and any disputes arising from your purchase will be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of [Your Country/Region]. Any legal action or proceeding related to your purchase must be brought in the courts of [Your Country/Region].
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Changes to Purchase Conditions</h2>
                <p>
                    fashionCulture reserves the right to update or modify these Purchase Conditions at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website. We encourage you to review these terms periodically to stay informed of any updates.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <style>
        main {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .purchase-conditions-section {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #444;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        strong {
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
